WHO   — Albedo — the whitening · purification
WHAT  — The cleansing after death — ablution, the washing-out of impurity until the matter shines white, the ‘silver’ of the Work.
WHERE — ALC · The Great Work  Framework inputs: Alchemy, catalogued by ROOT0  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
